%20in%20San%20Francisco%2C%20California.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ee9e6496b7920019ca2133%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221499%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMarc%20Andreessen%3Cp%3ESteve%20Jennings%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESilicon%20Valley%20billionaires%20buying%20up%20land%20in%20Solano%20County%2C%20California%2C%20could%20face%20big%20hurdles.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ELocal%20ordinances%2C%20environmental%20rules%2C%20and%20swirling%20federal%20questions%20could%20slow%20their%20roll.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%202017%2C%20Flannery%20Associates%20pitched%20an%20idea%20to%20create%20a%20new%2C%20walkable%20city%20in%20Solano%20County.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20conglomerate%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fflannery-silicon-valley-billionaires-build-new-california-city-solano-county-2023-8%5C%22%3ESilicon%20Valley%20billionaires%20buying%20up%20land%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20remote%20county%20outside%20of%20San%20Francisco%2C%20California%2C%20could%20be%20thwarted%20in%20its%20attempts%20to%20build%20a%20new%20city%20due%20to%20bureaucratic%20obstacles%20and%20local%20policies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20group%2C%20identified%20as%20Flannery%20Associates%20last%20week%2C%20is%20backed%20by%20Silicon%20Valley%20hotshots%20%E2%80%94%20including%20Marc%20Andreessen%20and%20Laurene%20Powell%20Jobs%20%E2%80%94%20and%20has%20been%20quietly%20buying%20up%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20acres%20in%20Solano%20County%2C%20California%2C%20since%202018.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20effort%20could%20face%20some%20significant%20logistical%20challenges%20tied%20to%20county%20ordinances%20and%20state%20policies%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F08%2F29%2Fbusiness%2Feconomy%2Fcalifornia-land-solano-county.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times%20reported.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.documentcloud.org%2Fdocuments%2F23927649-flannery-associates-lawsuit%3Fresponsive%3D1%26title%3D1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20court%20documents%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20company%20has%20spent%20some%20%24800%20million%20to%20buy%2052%2C000%20acres%20of%20farmland%2C%20offering%20up%20to%20%2415%2C000%20an%20acre.%20With%20the%20land%20purchased%2C%20the%20group's%20plot%20of%20land%20has%20started%20to%20encircle%20Travis%20Air%20Force%20Base%20nearby%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2Finvestors-bought-nearly-1-billion-in-land-near-a-california-air-force-base-officials-want-to-know-who-exactly-they-are-fd868e38%3Fmod%3Darticle_inline%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20The%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20at%20least%20one%20California%20developer%20has%20sounded%20the%20alarm%2C%20echoing%20a%20series%20of%20logistical%20reality%20checks%20that%20the%20group%20may%20soon%20face%20before%20breaking%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20hope%20they%20succeed%2C%26quot%3B%20Mark%20Friedman%2C%20real%20estate%20developer%20in%20Sacramento%2C%20told%20the%20Times.%20%26quot%3BBut%20this%20just%20seems%20like%20a%20lot%20of%20tech%20guys%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20and%20a%20ton%20of%20hubris%20diving%20into%20another%20business%20that%20they%20can't%20possibly%20understand.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20those%20challenges%20is%20that%20Solano%20County%20has%20a%20slow-growth%20ordinance%20in%20place%2C%20meaning%20that%20to%20start%20building%20projects%2C%20voters%20would%20have%20to%20approve%20getting%20rid%20of%20the%20law%20altogether%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEnvironmentally%2C%20potential%20construction%C2%A0would%20be%20accountable%20to%20California%20government%20rules%20dealing%20with%20air%2C%20water%2C%20and%20public%20utilities%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sfchronicle.com%2Fbayarea%2Farticle%2Fflannery-associates-land-investor-18327848.php%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eper%20the%20San%20Francisco%20Chronicle.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGetting%20the%20adequate%20approvals%20to%20begin%20construction%20in%20the%20area%20could%20delay%20any%20plans%20a%20decade%20or%20more%2C%20and%20require%20constant%20engagement%20with%20a%20local%20planning%20commission%2C%20the%20Times%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20still%20unclear%20what%20the%20group%20is%20planning.%20But%20in%202017%2C%20before%20beginning%20to%20buy%20the%20plots%2C%20the%20group%20pitched%20the%20idea%20of%20transforming%20part%20of%20Solano%20County%20into%20a%20walkable%20city%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F08%2F25%2Fbusiness%2Fland-purchases-solano-county.html%5C%22%3Ethe%20Times%20previously%20reported.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDemocratic%20Congressman%20John%20Garamendi%20%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%94%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ewho%20represents%20the%20county%3Cstrong%3E%20%E2%80%94%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20said%20he%20requested%20that%20the%20FBI%20and%20the%20Treasury%20look%20into%20what%20the%20purpose%20of%20the%20land%20purchases%20are%2C%20per%20the%20Times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20attorney%20for%20Flannery%20Associates%20did%20not%20immediately%20return%20Insider's%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey're%20also%20not%20the%20first%20Silicon%20Valley%20billionaires%20using%20their%20extreme%20wealth%20to%20chase%20bold%20developing%20ambitions%20only%20to%20be%20met%20with%20grinding%20bureaucracy.%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EElon%20Musk%20for%20years%20pitched%20his%20Boring%20Company%20tunnel%20as%20a%20method%20to%20eradicate%20%26quot%3Bsoul-destroying%20traffic%26quot%3B%20in%20major%20cities%20but%20has%20backtracked%20as%20local%20and%20federal%20officials%20have%20asked%20for%20permits%20and%20environmental%20reviews%20that%20the%20company%20didn't%20