ion%2C%20home%20to%20a%20significant%20Indian%20diaspora%2C%20primarily%20of%20Tamil%20origin%2C%20sourced%2040%25%20of%20its%20rice%20needs%20from%20India%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20non-basmati%20rice%20from%20India%20makes%20up%20about%2017%25%20of%20Singapore%E2%80%99s%20imported%20rice%2C%20the%20Singapore%20Food%20Agency%20said%20as%20per%20media%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20Indian%20ban%2C%20Singapore%20had%20been%20in%20talks%20with%20other%20countries%20to%20buy%20rice.%20During%20his%20visit%20to%20Singapore%2C%20Sri%20Lankan%20President%20Ranil%20Wickremesinghe%20was%20also%20approached%20about%20the%20possibility%20of%20rice%20procurement%20from%20the%20island%20nation%2C%20which%20continues%20to%20grapple%20with%20economic%20challenges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20ban%20on%20private%20wheat%20exports%20last%20year%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-ships-wheat-to-egypt-post-ban-gets-diplomatic-requests-from-12-nations-101652964766957.html%5C%22%3Eseveral%20nations%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20sought%20exemptions%2C%20with%20Egypt%20being%20among%20those%20granted%20the%20exemption.%20However%2C%20there%20was%20no%20public%20announcement%20made%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693364260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F30082706%2Fpierre-bamin-LdilhDx3sk-unsplash.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftrade%2Fsingapore-gets-rice-export-ban-exemption-due-to-very-close-strategic-partnership-india%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Singapore%20stands%20as%20one%20of%20India's%20closest%20allies%20in%20the%20Southeast%20Asian%20region%2C%20boasting%20trade%20ties%20exceeding%20%2430%20billion.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftrade%2Fsingapore-gets-rice-export-ban-exemption-due-to-very-close-s