n%20several%20films%20and%20were%20rumored%20to%20have%20been%20in%20a%20relationship.%20The%20sighting%20came%20after%20Dimple%20was%20seen%20leaving%20a%20theater%2C%20leading%20to%20speculation%20about%20whether%20she%20had%20watched%20Sunny's%20latest%20film%2C%20'Gadar%202'%2C%20or%20her%20son-in-law%20Akshay%20Kumar's%20film%2C%20'OMG%202'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fsunny-deol-dimple-kapadia-and-amrita-singh-spotted-together-fans-wonder-if-they-are-teaming-up-for-a-project-see-photos%2Farticleshow%2F103190473.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20About%20Punjab%2C%20Northeast%3A%20Supreme%20Court%20Questions%20J%26amp%3BK%20Bifurcation%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EJammu%20and%20Kashmir%20is%20not%20one-of-a-kind%20and%20Punjab%20and%20the%20Northeast%20have%20faced%20similar%20situations%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20pointed%20out%20today%2C%20questioning%20the%20need%20for%20bifurcation%20of%20the%20border%20state%20in%20August%202019.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%20also%20questioned%20how%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20power%20to%20bifurcate%20a%20state%20will%20not%20be%20%26quot%3Bmisused%26quot%3B%20once%20it%20is%20conceded%20to%20the%20Central%20government%20--%20a%20point%20that%20led%20to%20a%20discussion%20on%20why%20the%20question%20of%20bifurcation%20could%20not%20have%20been%20settled%20by%20parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20Day%2012%20of%20the%20hearing%20of%20a%20bunch%20of%20petitions%20challenging%20the%20scrapping%20of%20Article%20370%2C%20the%20Centre%20had%20argued%20that%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20was%20one%20of%20a%20kind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20Gujarat%20or%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20were%20to%20be%20bifurcated%2C%20then%20parameters%20would%20be%20different%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Solicitor%20General%20Tushar%20Mehta.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20SK%20Kaul%2C%20who%20was%20part%20of%20the%20five-judge%20constitutional%20bench%20led%20by%20Justice%20Chandrachud%2C%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20country%20has%20many%20states%20with%20borders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Mr%20Mehta%20responded%20that%20all%20the%20neighbouring%20countries%20are%20%26quot%3Bnot%20friendly%26quot%3B%20and%20there%20is%20a%20need%20to%20mainstream%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20in%20view%20of%20its%20history%20and%20current%20situation%20--%20%26quot%3Bstone%20pelting%2C%20strikes%2C%20deaths%20and%20terror%20attacks%26quot%3B%20--%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20weighed%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnce%20you%20concede%20that%20power%20to%20the%20Union%20in%20relation%20to%20every%20Indian%20state%2C%20how%20do%20you%20ensure%20that%20the%20kind%20of%20abuse%20they%20apprehended%20--%20this%20power%20will%20not%20be%20misused%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20not%20one%20of%20a%20kind%20situation%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20Justice%20Kaul.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20seen%20the%20northern%20border%20Punjab%20--%20very%20difficult%20times.%20Similarly%2C%20some%20states%20in%20the%20northeast...%20Tomorrow%20if%20there%20is%20a%20scenario%20that%20each%20of%20these%20states%20face%20this%20problem...%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDoes%20parliament%20have%20the%20power%20to%20convert%20an%20existing%20Indian%20state%20into%20a%20Union%20Territory%3F%26quot%3B%20questioned%20Chief%20Justice%20Chandrachud.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20said%20that%20even%20if%20the%20role%20of%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly%20only%20had%20a%20recommendatory%20role%20regarding%20Article%20370%20--%20which%20gave%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20its%20special%20status%20-%20that%20does%20not%20mean%20it%20can%20be%20overridden%20by%20the%20President%20of%20India.%20In%20an%20earlier%20hearing%2C%20the%20court%20had%20said%20the%20government%20will%20have%20to%20justify%20procedure%20it%20adopted%20to%20scrap%20the%20Article%20370%2C%20as%20it%20could%20not%20assume%20that%20%26quot%3Bend%20justifies%20the%20means%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693364160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-01%2Fastlnkkg_supreme-court-of-india-generic-getty_625x300_06_January_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-about-punjab-northeast-supreme-court-questions-j-k-bifurcation-4341159%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20is%20not%20one-of-a-kind%20and%20Punjab%20and%20the%20Northeast%20have%20faced%20similar%20situations%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20pointed%20out%20today%2C%20questioning%20the%20need%20for%20bifurcation%20of%20the%20border%20state%20in%20August%202019.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A20%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-about-punjab-northeast-supreme-court-questions-j-k-bifurcation-4341159%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-about-punjab-northeast-supreme-court-questions-j-k-bifurcation-4341159%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-about-punjab-northeast-supreme-court-questions-j-k-bifurcation-4341159%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BEntire%20Ladakh%20Knows...%26quot%3B%3A%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20After%20China%20Releases%20New%20Map%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ECongress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20today%20demanded%20a%20statement%20from%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20in%20response%20to%20China's%20release%20of%20a%20map%20that%20claims%20ownership%20of%20Aksai%20Chin%20and%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%2C%20which%20has%20been%20categorically%20rejected%20by%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20China%20released%20a%20new%20%26quot%3Bstandard%26quot%3B%20map%20that%20shows%20Aksai%20Chin%2C%20which%20it%20occupied%20in%20the%201962%20war%2C%20and%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%2C%20which%20it%20claims%20as%20South%20Tibet%2C%20as%20part%20of%20its%20territory.%20The%20map%20also%20shows%20the%20entire%20South%20China%20Sea%20as%20part%20of%20China%2C%20as%20it%20had%20in%20previous%20editions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20been%20saying%20for%20years%20that%20what%20the%20PM%20said%2C%20that%20not%20one%20inch%20of%20land%20was%20lost%20in%20Ladakh%2C%20is%20a%20lie.%20The%20entire%20Ladakh%20knows%20that%20China%20has%20transgressed.%20This%20map%20issue%20is%20very%20serious.%20They%20have%20taken%20away%20the%20land.%20PM%20should%20say%20something%20about%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20said%20while%20leaving%20for%20Karnataka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExternal%20Affairs%20Minister%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaking-absurd-claims-does-not-make-others-territory-yours-s-jaishankar-on-china-4339360%5C%22%3ES%20Jaishankar%20told%20NDTV%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20that%20the%20map%20meant%20nothing%20and%20China%20has%20a%20'habit'%20of%20releasing%20such%20maps.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChina%20has%20put%20out%20maps%20with%20territories%20(that%20are)%20not%20theirs.%20(It%20is%20an)%20old%20habit.%20Just%20by%20putting%20out%20maps%20with%20parts%20of%20India...%20this%20doesn't%20change%20in%20anything.%20Our%20government%20is%20very%20clear%20about%20what%20our%20territory.%20Making%20absurd%20claims%20does%20not%20make%20other%20people's%20territories%20yours%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20initiated%20protests%20through%20diplomatic%20channels%20over%20the%20%26quot%3Bstandard%26quot%3B%20map.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20reject%20the%20claims%20as%20they%20have%20no%20basis.%20Such%20steps%20by%20the%20Chinese%20side%20only%20complicate%20the%20resolution%20of%20the%20boundary%20question%2C%26quot%3B%20MEA%20spokesperson%20Arindam%20Bagchi%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20map%20has%20surfaced%20at%20a%20critical%20time%20as%20India%20gears%20up%20for%20the%20G20%20Summit%20scheduled%20for%20September%209-10.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20and%20Chinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20agreed%20to%20work%20for%20%26quot%3Bexpeditious%20de-escalation%26quot%3B%20along%20the%20entire%20Line%20of%20Actual%20Control%20(LAC)%20during%20their%20meeting%20at%20the%20BRICS%20summit%20in%20South%20Africa%20this%20month.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20announced%20new%20Chinese%20names%20for%2011%20places%20in%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20in%20early%20April.%20India%20rejected%20the%20renaming%2C%20asserting%20that%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20is%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20India%20and%20that%20assigning%20%26quot%3Binvented%26quot%3B%20names%20does%20not%20alter%20the%20reality%20that%20the%20northeastern%20state%20is%20under%20Indian%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20China's%20civil%20affairs%20ministry's%20third%20addition%20to%20the%20first%20batch%20of%20six%20places%20released%20in%202017%20and%20the%20second%20batch%20of%2015%20places%20released%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ties%20between%20India%20and%20China%20were%20severely%20strained%20by%20the%20eastern%20Ladakh%20border%20standoff%20that%20began%20in%20May%202020%20following%20which%20troops%20of%20both%20countries%20have%20been%20locked%20in%20an%20over%20three-year%20confrontation%20amid%20several%20talks%20of%20de-escalation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693363500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-04%2Foscnl41_rahul-gandhi-pti_625x300_16_April_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchina-map-pm-modi-rahul-gandhi-entire-ladakh-knows-rahul-gandhi-after-china-releases-new-map-4341186%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20today%20demanded%20a%20statement%20from%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20in%20response%20to%20China's%20release