ndia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Felon-musk-lifts-political-ad-ban-at-rebranded-twitter%2Farticleshow%2F103190124.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Felon-musk-lifts-political-ad-ban-at-rebranded-twitter%2Famp_articleshow%2F103190124.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Felon-musk-lifts-political-ad-ban-at-rebranded-twitter%2Famp_articleshow%2F103190124.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Google%20Launches%20Feature%20That%20Helps%20Book%20Cheaper%20Flights.%20Here's%20How%20It%20Works%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EGoogle%20Flights%20has%20introduced%20a%20new%20feature%20that%20will%20be%20beneficial%20for%20travellers%20aiming%20to%20save%20money%20on%20airfare.%20The%20new%20feature%2C%20which%20was%20officially%20announced%20through%20a%20blog%20post%20on%20Monday%20morning%2C%20offers%20guidance%20from%20Google%20on%20the%20most%20budget-friendly%20period%20for%20booking%20flights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20addition%20complements%20the%20existing%20price%20tracking%20alerts%20and%20a%20price%20guarantee%20choice%20that%20are%20already%20available%20on%20the%20platform.%20The%20tech%20giant%20has%20promised%20to%20give%20new%20insights%20on%20the%20%26quot%3Bcheapest%20time%20to%20book.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20searches%20with%20reliable%20trend%20data%2C%20you'll%20now%20see%20when%20prices%20have%20typically%20been%20lowest%20to%20book%20your%20chosen%20dates%20and%20destination%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fblog.google%2Fproducts%2Ftravel%2Fgoogle-flights-find-deals%2F%5C%22%3EGoogle%20in%20the%20blog%20post.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20does%20it%20work%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20the%20new%20insights%20could%20tell%20you%20that%20the%20cheapest%20time%20to%20book%20similar%20trips%20is%20usually%20two%20months%20before%20departure%2C%20and%20you're%20currently%20in%20that%20sweet%20spot.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOr%20you%20might%20learn%20that%20prices%20have%20usually%20dropped%20closer%20to%20takeoff%2C%20so%20you%20decide%20to%20wait%20before%20booking.%20Either%20way%2C%20you%20can%20make%20that%20decision%20with%20a%20greater%20sense%20of%20confidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20technology%20behemoth%20has%20also%20unveiled%20its%20flight%20booking%20trends%20for%202023%2C%20derived%20from%20historical%20pricing%20patterns%20observed%20on%20Google%20Flights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESecure%20a%20price%20guarantee%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20book%20one%20of%20these%20flights%2C%20we'll%20monitor%20the%20price%20every%20day%20before%20takeoff%2C%20and%20if%20the%20price%20does%20go%20down%2C%20we'll%20pay%20you%20back%20the%20difference%20via%20Google%20Pay%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20blog%20post%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20price%20guarantees%20are%20part%20of%20a%20pilot%20programme%20available%20for%20select%20Book%20on%20Google%20itineraries%20departing%20from%20the%20US.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20best%20time%20to%20book%20flights%20for%20Christmas%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Google%2C%20for%20trips%20starting%20in%20mid-December%2C%20you're%20most%20likely%20to%20find%20deals%20in%20early%20October.%20Average%20prices%20tend%20to%20be%20lowest%2071%20days%20before%20departure%2C%20a%20big%20change%20from%20our%202022%20insights%2C%20which%20found%20that%20average%20prices%20were%20lowest%20just%2022%20days%20before%20departure.%20And%20the%20typical%20low%20price%20range%20is%20now%2054-78%20days%20before%20takeoff.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20best%20time%20to%20book%20flights%20from%20the%20US%20to%20Europe%20is%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAverage%20prices%20have%20been%20at%20their%20lowest%2072%20days%20or%20more%20before%20departure.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20average%20airfares%20from%20the%20US%20to%20Europe%20only%20tend%20to%20increase%20over%20time%2C%20especially%20once%20you're%20about%2010%20weeks%20from%20departure.%20So%20if%20you%20want%20to%20dust%20off%20that%20passport%2C%20you%20should%20book%20your%20flight%20as%20soon%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693363260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F15sgivi8_flight-generic_625x300_28_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fgoogle-launches-new-feature-that-helps-book-cheaper-flights-heres-how-it-works-4341182%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20Monday%2C%20Google%20Flights%20unveiled%20a%20fresh%20feature%20that%20provides%20updated%20insights%20into%20the%20optimal%20timing%20for%20purchasing%20flight%20tickets.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A21%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fgoogle-launches-new-feature-that-helps-book-cheaper-flights-heres-how-it-works-4341182%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fgoogle-launches-new-feature-that-helps-book-cheaper-flights-heres-how-it-works-4341182%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fgoogle-launches-new-feature-that-helps-book-cheaper-flights-heres-how-it-works-4341182%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Road%20to%20ICC%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20begins%20with%20Asia%20Cup%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693363039000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103189972%2Cimgsize-138740.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fasia-cup%2Froad-to-icc-odi-world-cup-begins-with-asia-cup%2Farticleshow%2F103189945.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Time%20is%20running%20out.%20The%20Asia%20Cup%2C%20that%20starts%20in%20Multan%20on%20Wednesday%20with%20Pakistan%20taking%20on%20Nepal%2C%20is%20probably%20the%20last