%20a%20preparatory%20platform%20for%20the%20World%20Cup.%20Whichever%20World%20Cup%20is%20being%20held%20that%20year%2C%20be%20it%20in%20the%20ODI%20format%20or%20T20I%2C%20the%20Asia%20Cup%20is%20molded%20into%20the%20same%20format.%20Last%20year%2C%20when%20the%20Asia%20Cup%20was%20held%20in%20the%20UAE%2C%20it%20was%20the%20Sri%20Lanka%20cricket%20team%20that%20emerged%20triumphant%2C%20winning%20the%20title%20in%20the%20T20%20format.%20But%2C%20this%20time%20around%2C%20the%20Asian%20sides%20will%20battle%20it%20out%20in%20the%2050-over%20format%20of%20the%20game.%20But%2C%20why%20is%20it%20so%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20'Format'%20of%20Asia%20Cup%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20Asia%20Cup%20boasts%20of%20some%20of%20the%20top%20sides%20in%20the%20world%2C%20including%20India%2C%20Pakistan%2C%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20Afghanistan%2C%20Bangladesh%2C%20etc.%2C%20the%20tournament%20is%20still%20seen%20as%20a%20'preparatory'%20event.%20These%20days%2C%20the%20Asian%20Cricket%20Council%20(ACC)%20organises%20the%20Asia%20Cup%20the%20same%20year%20when%20the%20World%20Cup%20is%20taking%20place.%20Whichever%20format%20of%20the%20World%20Cup%20it%20is%20(T20%20or%2050-over)%2C%20the%20Asia%20Cup%20takes%20that%20form.%20Considering%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20the%20game%20has%20grown%2C%20Asian%20teams%20do%20tend%20to%20benefit%20from%20this%20approach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tournament%20started%20all%20the%20way%20back%20in%201984%20in%20the%20ODI%20format%20but%20things%20changed%20after%20the%20introduction%20of%20T20s.%20The%20last%20ODI%20Asia%20Cup%20was%20held%20in%202019%2C%20the%20same%20year%20the%20last%20World%20Cup%20in%20the%20format%20was%20held.%20It%20was%20the%20Indian%20team%20that%20clinched%20the%20title%20that%20year.%20But%2C%20it%20wasn't%20even%20a%20full-strength%20Indian%20side%20that%20participated%20in%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20team's%20talismanic%20batter%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Virat%20Kohli%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F967-virat-kohli-playerprofile%5C%22%3EVirat%20Kohli%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20also%20the%20team's%20captain%20back%20then%2C%20didn't%20participate%20in%20the%20event%2C%20giving%20charge%20to%20his%20deputy%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rohit%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F857-rohit-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERohit%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20fact%2C%20in%20a%20game%2C%20even%20Rohit%20decided%20to%20rest%20himself%2C%20giving%20charge%20to%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22MS%20Dhoni%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F700-ms-dhoni-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMS%20Dhoni%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20the%202023%20edition%2C%20it%20will%20be%20co-hosted%20by%20Pakistan%20and%20Sri%20Lanka.%20This%20event%20will%20also%20mark%20the%20debut%20of%20Nepal%20in%20the%20tournament.%20Nepal%20booked%20their%20ticket%20to%20the%20event%20by%20winning%20the%20inaugural%20ACC%20Men's%20Premier%20Cup%202023%2C%20where%20they%20defeated%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%20in%20the%20final.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693359660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fa7d620ns_asia-cup-2023_625x300_19_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fasia-cup-2023%2Fwhy-asia-cup-2023-will-be-held-in-odi-format-and-not-t20i-4338987%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Asia%20Cup%20started%20as%20a%20tournament%20which%20was%20held%20in%20ODI%20format%20but%20in%20recent%20editions%2C%20it%20has%20also%20been%20held%20in%20the%20T20%20format.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fasia-cup-2023%2Fwhy-asia-cup-2023-will-be-held-in-odi-format-and-not-t20i-4338987%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fasia-cup-2023%2Fwhy-asia-cup-2023-will-be-held-in-odi-format-and-not-t20i-4338987%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fasia-cup-2023%2Fwhy-asia-cup-2023-will-be-held-in-odi-format-and-not-t20i-4338987%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bumrah%20Won't%20Be%20Used%20At%20Full%20Throttle%20In%20Asia%20Cup%3F%20Dravid%20Reveals%20Approach%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20return%20of%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Jasprit%20Bumrah%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1724-jasprit-bumrah-playerprofile%5C%22%3EJasprit%20Bumrah%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20been%20the%20biggest%20news%20in%20Indian%20cricket%20in%20recent%20times.%20The%20ace%20pacer%2C%20once%20the%20bowling%20spearhead%20of%20team%20team%2C%20had%20been%20out%20of%20action%20by%20lower%20back%20injury%20and%20subsequent%20rehabilitation%20for%20the%20last%2011%20months.%20However%2C%20his%20comeback%20against%20Ireland%20in%20the%20T20I%20series%20had%20Indian%20cricket%20fans%20going%20gaga%20over%20his%20return.%20A%20big%20test%20awaits%20for%20him%20in%20the%20form%20of%20Asia%20Cup%20and%20the%20World%20Cup.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPlaying%20a%20T20I%20match%2C%20where%20a%20maximum%20of%20four%20overs%20can%20be%20bowler%20by%20a%20player%2C%20and%20an%20ODI%20match%2C%20where%20the%20strike%20bowler%20of%20the%20team%20is%20expected%20to%20bowl%2010%20intense%20overs%20is%20different.%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20head%20coach%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rahul%20Dravid%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F174-rahul-dravid-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERahul%20Dravid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20his%20pre-departure%20press%20conference%20before%20boarding%20a%20flight%20to%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20hinted%20that%20Bumrah%20will%20be%20slowed%20eased%20into%20full%20action.%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20great%20to%20have%20them%20(Bumrah%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Prasidh%20Krishna%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F107509-prasidh-krishna-playerprofile%5C%22%3EPrasidh%20Krishna%3C%2Fa%3E)%20back%20and%20see%20them%20bowling%20well.%20Jasprit%20is%20someone%20we%20have%20missed%20a%20lot%20in%20the%20past%20two%20years%20he%20hasn't%20played%20much.%20We%20will%20ease%20him%20into%20it%20slowly.%20Ireland%20was%20a%20good%20opportunity%20to%20ease%20him%20in.%20Now%20we%20have%20a%20whole%20month%20to%20build%20that%20up%20before%20the%20World%20Cup.%20The%20duo's%20return%20gives%20us%20more%20options%20in%20the%20pace%20bowling%20department%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHome%20advantage%20not%20there%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20India%20captain%20also%20felt%20that%20the%20home%20advantage%20for%20the%20sub-continent%20teams%20has%20reduced%20significantly%20in%20the%20last%20decade%2C%20owing%20to%20foreign%20players%20regularly%20competing%20in%20the%20conditions%2C%20with%20IPL%20a%20major%20draw.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20whole%20thing%20of%20home%20advantage%20at%20sub-continent%20has%20reduced%20to%20a%20large%20extent%20over%20the%20past%2010-12%20years.%20People%20come%20and%20play%20here%20so%20much%2C%20especially%20tournaments%20like%20the%20IPL.%20They%20are%20here%20for%20two-three%20months%20getting%20used%20to%20conditions.%20It%20will%20be%20a%20tight%20tournament%2C%26quot%3B%20Dravid%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693359420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fbjrgg6pg_dravid-bumrah_625x300_13_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fasia-cup-2023%2Fjasprit-bumrah-wont-be-used-at-full-throttle-in-asia-cup-2023-rahul-dravid-drops-the-slowly-word-4340356%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20return%20of%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%20has%20been%20the%20biggest%20news%20in%20Indian%20cricket%20in%20recent%20times.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fasia-cup-2023%2Fjasprit-bumrah-wont-be-used-at-full-throttle-in-a