Bagchi%20on%20Tuesday%20in%20response%20to%20media%20queries%20on%20rice%20export%20to%20Singapore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFormal%20orders%20in%20this%20regard%20will%20be%20issued%20shortly%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Bagchi%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20on%20August%2027%20introduced%20additional%20safeguards%20on%20exports%20of%20basmati%20rice%20so%20as%20to%20prevent%20exports%20of%20non-basmati%20white%20rice%2C%20which%20is%20presently%20under%20the%20prohibited%20category.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20Sunday%2C%20the%20government%20said%20it%20has%20received%20credible%20field%20reports%20regarding%20misclassification%20and%20illegal%20export%20of%20non-basmati%20white%20rice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20has%20been%20reported%20that%20non-basmati%20white%20rice%20is%20being%20exported%20under%20the%20HS%20codes%20of%20parboiled%20rice%20and%20basmati%20rice%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20government%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20the%20export%20of%20non-basmati%20white%20rice%20was%20prohibited%20from%20July%2020%20to%20check%20the%20domestic%20prices%20and%20ensure%20domestic%20food%20security.%20The%20government%20noticed%20that%20despite%20restrictions%20put%20on%20certain%20varieties%2C%20rice%20exports%20have%20been%20high%20during%20the%20current%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20central%20government%20on%20July%2020%20amended%20the%20rice%20export%20norms%20putting%20the%20non-basmati%20white%20rice%20in%20the%20%26quot%3Bprohibited%26quot%3B%20category.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20export%20policy%20relating%20to%20non-basmati%20white%20rice%20(semi-milled%20or%20wholly%20milled%20rice%2C%20whether%20or%20not%20polished%20or%20glazed)%20has%20been%20revised%20from%20%26quot%3Bfree%26quot%3B%20to%20%26quot%3Bprohibited%26quot%3B%20and%20it%20has%20come%20into%20force%20immediately%2C%20a%20Directorate%20General%20of%20Foreign%20Trade%20(DGFT)%20notification%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20t