%20to%20see%20funny%20reflections%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20finished%20product%2C%20Wardle%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20side%20of%20the%20truck%20looks%20less%20like%20a%20cohesive%20design%20and%20more%20like%20%26quot%3Bfour%20flat%20panels%20that%20happen%20to%20be%20adjacent%20to%20each%20other.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20potential%20issue%20he%20foresees%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-cybertruck-might-be-fingerprint-magnet-stainless-steel-body-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efingerprints%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnyone%20who's%20owned%20a%20stainless%20steel%20fridge%20knows%20they%20are%20a%20magnet%20for%20grime%20and%20are%20a%20nightmare%20to%20keep%20clean.%20Now%20imagine%20that%20issue%20on%20practically%20every%20surface%20of%20your%20truck%2C%20which%20is%20routinely%20exposed%20to%20nasty%20environments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20isn't%20sure%20any%20of%20it%20will%20matter%20to%20the%20Cybertruck's%20most%20enthusiastic%20fans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMaybe%20customers%20are%20going%20to%20like%20them%20to%20get%20all%20grubby%20and%20dirty%20and%20have%20that%20sort%20of%20'Star%20Wars'%20look%20about%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20for%20more%20traditional%20folks%2C%20they%20might%20be%20bothered%20about%20paying%20probably%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20for%20this%20car%20and%20finding%20that%20the%20doors%20and%20the%20fenders%20look%20like%20they're%20warped.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EMusk%20knows%20the%20Cybertruck%20needs%20to%20be%20perfect%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20himself%20has%20indicated%20he's%20concerned%20about%20how%20the%20Cybertruck%20will%20look%20in%20its%20final%20form%2C%20saying%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2023%2F08%2F24%2Felon-musk-memo-on-cybertruck-manufacturing-challenges.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eleaked%20email%20to%20staff%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20week%3A%20%26quot%3BDue%20to%20the%20nature%20of%20Cybertruck%2C%20which%20is%20made%20of%20bright%20metal%20with%20mostly%20straight%20edges%2C%20any%20dimensional%20variation%20shows%20up%20like%20a%20sore%20thumb.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe's%20right.%20For%20years%2C%20Tesla%20buyers%20have%20complained%20about%20glaringly%20misaligned%20body%20panels%2C%20and%20those%20kinds%20of%20issues%20stick%20out%20in%20early%20Cybertruck%20photos.%20Just%20look%20at%20Musk's%20recent%20post%20again%2C%20and%20zero%20in%20this%20time%20on%20the%20spot%20by%20the%20headlight.%20Instead%20of%20a%20clean%20edge%2C%20you%20see%20a%20weird%20gap.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETesla%20has%20always%20been%20able%20to%20get%20away%20with%20a%20level%20of%20imperfection%2C%20thanks%20to%20a%20rabid%20fanbase%20that%20cares%20more%20about%20cutting-edge%20technology%20than%20craftsmanship.%20But%20the%20Cybertruck%20is%20a%20different%20ballgame%2C%20Fiorani%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMusk%20has%20learned%20from%20his%20past%20mistakes%20%E2%80%93%20he%20understands%20that%20people%20will%20scrutinize%20this%20vehicle%2C%26quot%3B%20Fiorani%20said.%20%26quot%3BThen%20you%20add%20in%20the%20complexity%20of%20a%20vehicle%20like%20the%20Cybertruck%2C%20where%20the%20smallest%20blemish%20will%20show%20up%20as%20a%20glaring%20error.%20He%20recognizes%20the%20issue%20with%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-cybertrucks-stainless-steel-will-always-be-a-little-smudgy-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693336479000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ee3b70d1f80d00192f1fe2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-cybertrucks-stainless-steel-will-always-be-a-little-smudgy-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20heavy%20use%20of%20stainless%20steel%20on%20Tesla%20Cybertruck's%20exterior%20will%20make%20it%20hard%20to%20keep%20looking%20pr