08.2023%2C%20a%20firing%20incident%20occurred%20between%20armed%20miscreants%20in%20the%20adjoining%20villages%20of%20Naransena%2C%20resulting%20in%2002%20fatalities%20and%2007%20individuals%20sustaining%20bullet%20or%20splinter%20injuries.%20District%20Police%2C%20AR%2C%20Army%2C%20and%20CAPF%20forces%20deployed%20in%20the%20area%20promptly%20responded%20and%20managed%20to%20bring%20the%20situation%20under%20control.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhousabung%20is%20only%205%20kms%20away%20from%20Naransena.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20ten%20days%20ago%2C%20three%20individuals%20lost%20their%20lives%20in%20the%20Kuki%20village%20of%20Thowai%20Kuki.%20The%20victims%20were%20identified%20as%20Thangkhokai%20Haokip%20(35)%2C%20Jamkhogin%20Haokip%20(26)%2C%20and%20Hollenson%20Baite%20(24).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20ongoing%20violence%20in%20Manipur%2C%20over%20150%20people%20have%20died%2C%20and%20less%20than%20half%20of%20the%20deceased%E2%80%99s%20families%20have%20received%20a%20compensation%20of%20Rs%205%20lakh%20as%20against%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fkin-of-manipur-violence-victims-to-get-rs-10-lakh-relief-8637717%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520government%2520on%2520Tuesday%2520announced%2Cstate%2520to%2520review%2520the%2520situation.%5C%22%3Epromised%3C%2Fa%3E%20Rs%2010%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJangminlun%E2%80%99s%20family%20has%20not%20yet%20registered%20a%20first%20information%20report%20(FIR)%2C%20till%20the%20time%20of%20going%20to%20press.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20in%20the%20Churachandpur%20district%2C%204%2C036%20zero%20FIRs%20have%20been%20registered%2C%20including%2012%20crimes%20against%20women%20%E2%80%93%20six%20each%20at%20the%20Churachandpur%20police%20station%20and%20women%E2%80%99s%20police%20station.%20Furthermore%2C%201%2C283%20regular%20FIRs%20have%20been%20registered%2C%20and%201%2C622%20FIRs%20originally%20filed%20in%20other%20districts%20have%20been%20converted%20into%20regular%20FIRs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20this%20incident%20transpired%20on%20the%20same%20day%20as%20the%20Manipur%20government%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmanipur-assembly-monsoon-session-anusuiya-uikey%5C%22%3Efirst%20assembly%20session%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20during%20which%20three%20resolutions%20were%20passed%20in%20the%20House%2C%20as%20reported%20by%20the%20governor%E2%80%99s%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20resolutions%20included%20a%20commitment%20to%20maintaining%20harmony%20without%20discrimination%2C%20an%20aspiration%20for%20peace%20through%20dialogue%2C%20and%20an%20appeal%20to%20renounce%20violence.%20Opposition%20MLAs%20from%20the%20Congress%20party%20demanded%20a%20two-minute%20silence%20in%20honour%20of%20those%20killed%20in%20the%20violence%20and%20sought%20an%20extension%20of%20the%20single-day%20session%20to%20five%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Speaker%20Thokchom%20Satyabrata%20Singh%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmanipur-assemblys-one-day-session-adjourned-after-11-minutes%5C%22%3Eadjourned%20the%20session%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%2011%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693332690000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F29233841%2Fimage-1264.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-fresh-violence-erupts-in-churachandpur-one-person-from-the-kuki-zo-community-dies%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jangminlun%20Gangte%20was%20shot%20in%20a%20firing%20incident%20in%20the%20adjoining%20villages%20of%20Narasena.%20His%20cousin%20alleged%20that%20he%20was%20killed%20by%20the%20Manipur%20police%20commandos%20during%20the%20attack%20on%20their%20village%2C%20Khousabung%2C%20which%20is%20only%205%20kilometres%20away%20from%20Naransena.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-fresh-vi