%20designed%20the%20lander%20module%20of%20Chandrayaan-3%2C%20the%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrivedi%20allegedly%20posed%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bassistant%20chairman%26quot%3B%20of%20ISRO's%20%26quot%3BAncient%20Science%20Application%20department%26quot%3B%20and%20even%20produced%20a%20fake%20appointment%20letter%20dated%20February%2026%2C%202022%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20thorough%20investigation%20revealed%20that%20the%20man%20was%20in%20no%20way%20connected%20to%20ISRO's%20Chandrayaan-3%20mission%20and%20had%20made%20false%20claims%20of%20being%20an%20ISRO%20employee%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20police%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20even%20produced%20a%20fake%20letter%20about%20being%20the%20%26quot%3Bspace%20research%20member%26quot%3B%20for%20ISRO's%20next%20project%20called%20%26quot%3Bmercury%20force%20in%20space%26quot%3B%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20spread%20fake%20messages%20regarding%20ISRO%20despite%20not%20having%20contributed%20to%20the%20ambitious%20project%2C%20thereby%20harming%20the%20reputation%20of%20the%20institution%2C%20the%20statement%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Surat%20city%20crime%20branch%20lodged%20an%20FIR%20against%20the%20accused%20under%20sections%20419%20(cheating%20by%20impersonation)%2C%20465%20(forgery)%2C%20468%20(forgery%20for%20purpose%20of%20cheating)%2C%20and%20471%20(using%20forged%20document%20as%20genuine)%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693325880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F04f2nnlo_chandrayaan-lander-vikram_650x400_17_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgujarat-man-poses-as-scientist-who-designed-chandrayaan-3-lander-arrested-4340588%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%2