call-for-unclassified-strategy-on-china-as-foreign-secretary-james-clevery-visits-for-first-time-in-five-years-12950308%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fmps-call-for-unclassified-strategy-on-china-as-foreign-secretary-james-clevery-visits-for-first-time-in-five-years-12950308%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Chandrayaan-3%20Mission%20Detects%20Sulphur%20On%20Moon's%20South%20Pole%3A%20ISRO%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20first-ever%20on-site%20measurements%20of%20the%20south%20polar%20region%20of%20the%20moon%20have%20confirmed%20the%20presence%20of%20sulphur%20on%20Earth's%20only%20natural%20satellite%2C%20ISRO%20said%20today.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20measurements%20were%20made%20by%20the%20Laser-Induced%20Breakdown%20Spectroscopy%20(LIBS)%20instrument%20onboard%20Chandrayaan-3's%20rover%2C%20Pragyan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20space%20agency%20said%20the%20in-situ%20measurements%20confirmed%20the%20presence%20of%20sulphur%20in%20the%20region%20%E2%80%9Cunambiguously%E2%80%9D%2C%20which%20was%20not%20feasible%20using%20the%20instruments%20onboard%20the%20orbiters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20presence%20of%20oxygen%2C%20calcium%20and%20iron%20has%20also%20been%20detected%20and%20the%20hunt%20for%20hydrogen%20is%20underway.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EChandrayaan-3%20Mission%3A%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnIn-situ%20scientific%20experiments%20continue%20.....%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnLaser-Induced%20Breakdown%20Spectroscope%20(LIBS)%20instrument%20onboard%20the%20Rover%20unambiguously%20confirms%20the%20presence%20of%20Sulphur%20(S)%20in%20the%20lunar%20surface%20near%20the%20south%20pole%2C%20through%20first-ever%20in-situ%20measurements.%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FvDQmByWcSL%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FvDQmByWcSL%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ISRO%20(%40isro)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fisro%2Fstatus%2F1696529346872451541%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%2029%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPreliminary%20analyses%2C%20graphically%20represented%2C%20have%20unveiled%20the%20presence%20of%20Aluminum%20(Al)%2C%20Sulphur%20(S)%2C%20Calcium%20(Ca)%2C%20Iron%20(Fe)%2C%20Chromium%20(Cr)%2C%20and%20Titanium%20(Ti)%20on%20the%20lunar%20surface.%20Further%20measurements%20have%20revealed%20the%20presence%20of%20manganese%20(Mn)%2C%20silicon%20(Si)%2C%20and%20oxygen%20(O).%20Thorough%20investigation%20regarding%20the%20presence%20of%20Hydrogen%20is%20underway%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20ISRO%20statement%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELIBS%20conducted%20measurements%20of%20the%20elemental%20composition%20of%20the%20lunar%20surface.%20It%20conducted%20the%20analysis%20by%20exposing%20the%20materials%20to%20intense%20laser%20pulses.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agency%20had%20said%20yesterday%20that%20the%20rover%20had%20been%20rerouted%20safely%20after%20encountering%20a%20four-meter%20crater%20on%20the%20lunar%20surface.%20The%20crater%20had%20been%20spotted%20three%20metres%20from%20the%20edge.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20had%20created%20history%20on%20August%2023%20by%20becoming%20the%20first%20country%20to%20achieve%20a%20soft%20landing%20near%20the%20south%20pole%20of%20the%20moon.%20It%20had%20also%20joined%20an%20elite%20club%20of%20countries%20-%20Russia%2C%20the%20US%20and%20China%20-%20to%20have%20successfully%20landed%20on%20the%20lunar%20surface.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EISRO's%20success%20had%20come%20days%20after%20Russia's%20Luna-25%20spacecraft%20had%20crashed%20on%20the%20moon's%20surface%20following%20an%20engine%20failure.%20Russia%20was%20also%20aiming%20to%20land%20near%20the%20lunar%20south%20pole.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Vikram%20lander%20and%20Pragyan%20rover%20have%20a%20mission%20life%20of%201%20lunar%20day%2C%20which%20is%20equivalent%20to%2014%20days%20on%20Earth.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693324440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fa9j292js_chandrayaan-pragyan-rollout_625x300_25_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchandrayaan-3-mission-detects-sulphur-on-moons-south-pole-isro-4340331%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20first-ever%20on-site%20measurements%20of%20the%20south%20polar%20region%20of%20the%20moon%20have%20confirmed%20the%20presence%20of%20sulphur%20on%20Earth's%20only%20natural%20satellite%2C%20ISRO%20said%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchandrayaan-3-mission-detects-sulphur-on-moons-south-pole-isro-4340331%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchandrayaan-3-mission-detects-sulphur-on-moons-south-pole-isro-4340331%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchandrayaan-3-mission-detects-sulphur-on-moons-south-pole-isro-4340331%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Delhi%20HC%20Dismisses%20PIL%20Seeking%20Disclosure%20of%20EVM%20Serial%20Numbers%20and%20Manufacturers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F06%2F02121850%2Fdelhi-high-court-1558979556.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Delhi%20high%20court%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20August%2029%2C%20dismissed%20a%20public%20interest%20litigation%20(PIL)%20seeking%20disclosure%20of%20electronic%20voting%20machine%20(EVM)%20serial%20numbers%20and%20manufacturers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20plea%20requested%20that%20these%20details%20should%20be%20provided%20to%20the%20representatives%20of%20the%20political%20parties%20before%20the%20first-level%20checking%20(FLC)%20is%20completed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20the%20FLC%20of%20the%20machines%20is%20the%20first%20step%20of%20the%20verification%20process.%20However%2C%20the%20petition%20raised%20doubts%20over%20the%20credibility%20of%20the%20verification%20process.%20It%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20FLC%20was%20completed%20even%20though%20the%20Congress%20party%20boycotted%20the%20process%2C%20saying%20that%20they%20were%20not%20provided%20with%20any%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20FLC%20is%20over%2C%20the%20machines%20are%20sealed%20and%20stored%20in%20designated%20warehouses%20and%20opened%20only%20when%20the%20poll%20process%20begins%2C%20starting%20with%20the%20notification%20of%20the%20polls.%20The%20FLC%20for%20Delhi%20has%20been%20completed%2C%20the%20counsel%20for%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20told%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petition%20was%20filed%20by%20Delhi%20Pradesh%20Congress%20Committee%20chief%2C%20Anil%20Choudhary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20these%20crucial%20details%2C%20what%20is%20the%20point%20of%20simply%20going%20to%20look%20at%20the%20machines%3F%20All%20machines%20look%20the%20same.%20In%20order%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20the%20serial%20number%20of%20the%20machine%20matches%20with%20our%20list%2C%20they%20have%20to%20provide%20%5Bus%20with%5D%20the%20serial%20numbers%2C%20model%2C%20manufacturer.%20They%20are%20refusing%20to%20give%20us%20information%20about%20the%20basic%20hardware%20that%20will%20be%20used%20in%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%E2%80%9D%20one%20of%20the%20counsels%20for%20the%20petitioner%20told%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petition%20says%20that%20letters%20were%20sent%2C%20inviting%20representatives%20of%20various%20political%20parties%20for%20the%20preparatory%20meetings.%20These%20meetings%20were%20scheduled%20to%20be%20held%20between%20July%206%20and%2012.%20These%20letters%20were%20issued%20by%20various%20%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ESub-Divisional%20Magistrates%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20who%20are%20authorised%20to%20conduct%20the%20FLC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%20said%20that%20the%20EVM%20and%20the%20voter%20verifiable%20paper%20audit%20trails%20(VVPATs)%20would%20be%20checked%20at%20the%20respective%20district%20headquarters%20in%20different%20parts%20of%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20rather%20than%20addressing%20the%20concerns%20raised%20by%20the%20party%2C%20the%20Chief%20Electoral%20Officer%2C%20Delhi%2C%20went%20ahead%20with%20finalising%20the%20dates%20for%20the%20FLC%20which%20was%20to%20be%20conducted%20from%20July%2015%20to%20July%2030.%20And%20since%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20concerns%20were%20not%20addressed%2C%20the%20Congress%20boycotted%20the%20FLC%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20SDMs%20issued%20letters%20to%20the%20Congress%20party%2C%20requesting%20them%20to%20participate.%20But%20they%20didn%E2%80%99t.%20And%20the%20FLC%20continued%20without%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FLC%20has%20been%20completed%20for%20Delhi%2C%20Kerala%2C%20and%20Jharkhand%2C%20and%20is%20underway%20in%20five%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petitioner%20filed%20a%20representation%20before%20the%20Chief%20Electoral%20Officer%2C%20saying%20that%20without%20this%20information%2C%20they%20will%20be%20unable%20to%20train%20their%20officers.%20These%20officers%20would%20be%20involved%20in%20the%20election%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Electoral%20Officer%2C%20Ranbir%20Singh%2C%20heard%20the%20representatives%3B%20however%2C%20he%20did%20not%20address%20any%20of%20the%20issues%20raised%20by%20the%20party%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20entire%20attempt%20of%20the%20Election%20Commission%20is%20highly%20surreptitious.%20The%20procedure%20followed%20for%20the%20commencement%20of%20the%20FLC%20was%20not%20transparent%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20PIL.%20Only%20oral%20assurances%20were%20made%20by%20the%20officers%20concerned.%20The%20Chief%20Electoral%20Officer%20rejected%20the%20contentions%20of%20the%20Congress%20in%20a%20written%20reply%20on%20August%2010%2C%20forcing%20the%20petitioner%20to%20move%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petitioner%20also%20pointed%20out%2C%20citing%20circulars%20of%202017%20and%202022%2C%20that%20for%20the%20elections%20held%20in%20the%20past%2C%20the%20FLC%20process%20had%20started%20six%20months%20in%20advance%2C%20as%20per%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20instructions.%20However%2C%20this%20time%20the%20process%20has%20been%20advanced%20by%20three%20months%2C%20arbitrarily%2C%20by%20the%20Chief%20Electoral%20Officer%2C%20making%20the%20%E2%80%9Cstakeholder%20political%20parties%20a%20silent%20spectator%20to%20the%20entire%20process%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20counsel%20for%20the%20Election%20Commission%20told%20the%20court%20that%20the%20FLC%20process%20is%20being%20conducted%20as%20per%20the%20election%20manual%2C%20which%20has%20not%20been%20challenged%20by%20the%20petitioners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20manual%20says%20that%20after%20the%20%5Bfirst-level%5D%20checking%20is%20done%2C%20the%20machine%20is%20sealed%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20the%20representatives%20and%20details%20are%20provided%20after%20that.%20If%20the%20details%20are%20to%20be%20provided%20before%20the%20FLC%2C%20then%20it%20will%20be%20a%20cumbersome%20exercise%20and%20the%20FLC%20across%20the%20country%20will%20have%20to%20start%20afresh.%20This%20is%20not%20a%20minor%20exercise%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJagdeep%20Chokar%20from%20the%20Association%20for%20Democratic%20reforms%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20FLC%20is%20the%20first%20step%20in%20the%20process%20of%20electronic%20voting.%20The%20entire%20process%20has%20to%20be%20and%20should%20be%20transparent%20and%20open%20to%20scrutiny.%20It%20is%20imperative%20that%20the%20outcome%20of%20the%20FLC%20be%20shared%2C%20otherwise%20the%20curtain%20of%20opacity%20will%20continue%20to%20hide%20the%20functioning%20of%20the%20EVMs.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20reasoned%20court%20order%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20uploaded%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693324304000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F06%2F02121850%2Fdelhi-high-court-1558979556.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fdelhi-hc-dismisses-pil-seeking-disclosure-of-evm-serial-numbers-and-manufacturers%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20plea%20requested%20that%20these%20details%20should%20be%20provided%20to%20the%20representatives%20of%20the%20political%20parties%20before%20the%20first-level%20checking%20is%20completed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fdelhi-hc-dismisses-pil-seeking-disclosure-of-evm-serial-numbers-and-manufacturers%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Police%20seek%20help%20identifying%20child's%20body%20found%20in%20German%20river%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693324266000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F100A7%2Fproduction%2F_130930756_dscf2150_edit_halbrechtsbd.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-66650999%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Interpol%20says%20%26quot%3Bsomeone%2C%20somewhere%20knows%20something%26quot%3B%20about%20the%20boy%2C%20whose%20body%20was%20found%20in%20Germany.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A53%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-66650999%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-66650999.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-66650999.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ektaa%20Kapoor%20to%20be%20conferred%20at%20Emmys%202023%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693324168000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103183012%2Cimgsize-39742.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A