ge1-2.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20light%20of%20new%20scientific%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flink.springer.com%2Farticle%2F10.1007%2Fs11104-023-06191-4%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eresearch%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20nano%20urea%20(NU)%20dream%20is%20fading.%20A%20recent%20paper%20by%20Max%20Frank%20and%20Soren%20Husted%20from%20the%20University%20of%20Copenhagen%20clearly%20states%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20observe%20that%20NU%20is%20a%20poorly%20described%20product%20with%20no%20scientifically%20proven%20effects.%20The%20product%20is%20marketed%20with%20misleading%20and%20wrong%20statements%20about%20its%20fertiliser%20efficiency%2C%20the%20under-lying%20plant%20uptake%20pathways%2C%20and%20the%20environmental%20friendliness.%E2%80%9D%20Therefore%2C%20the%20NU%20project%20is%2C%20at%20best%2C%20a%20paper%20tiger.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20only%20two%20foreign%20scientists%2C%20but%20studies%20from%20India%E2%80%99s%20public%20agricultural%20research%20institutes%20that%20confirm%20NU%E2%80%99s%20shortcomings.%20Despite%20this%2C%20the%20government%20boldly%20announced%20that%20it%20would%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-aims-end-urea-imports-2025-pegs-fy23-fertilisers-subsidy-272-bln-2022-11-02%2F%5C%22%3Eend%20urea%20imports%20by%202025.%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWhat%20is%20nano%20urea%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Indian%20government%20has%20a%2041%25%20stake%20in%20the%20Indian%20Farmers%20Fertilizer%20Cooperative%20(IFFCO)%2C%20a%20fertiliser%20manufacturer%20and%20importing%20company.%20Some%20time%20ago%2C%20the%20cooperative%20announced%20the%20invention%20of%20nano-sized%20urea%2C%20claiming%20that%20its%20absorption%20by%20plants%20is%20higher%20and%20that%20the%20fertiliser%20increases%20crop%20yields%20by%208%25.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20also%20claim%20that%20instead%20of%20using%20a%20regular%2045%20kg%20bag%20of%20urea%20(45%20kg%20urea%20or%2020.7%20kg%20of%20nitrogen)%2C%20farmers%20can%20now%20use%20a%20500%20ml%20bottle%20with%204%25%20nano%20urea%20(43%20g%20urea%20or%2020%20g%20of%20nitrogen)%20on%20their%20crops%20and%20expect%20higher%20yields.%20The%20%E2%80%9Cmagic%E2%80%9D%20behind%20this%20transition%20is%20the%20fact%20that%20plants%20are%20better%20suited%20to%20take%20up%20the%20nanoparticles%2C%20and%20this%20formulation%20also%20prevents%20leaching%20or%20fertiliser%20run-offs%2C%20hence%20slightly%20better%20for%20the%20plants%2C%20farmers%E2%80%99%20pockets%20and%20the%20environment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIFFCO%20claims%20that%20NU%20is%20about%201%2C035%20times%20more%20efficiently%20taken%20up%20by%20crops%20and%20compared%20to%20conventional%20urea%2C%20it%20is%20that%20much%20more%20effective%20in%20both%20soil%20application%20and%20foliar%20spray.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESubsequently%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnewsonair.gov.in%2FNews%3Ftitle%3DUnion-Minister-Amit-Shah-to-be-on-two-day-visit-to-Gujarat%26id%3D466002%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Elaunched%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20first%20nano%20fertiliser%20production%20plant%20in%20Gujarat%20with%20our%20tax%20rupees.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20plant%20is%20making%20nano-DAP%20(di-ammonium%20phosphate)%2C%20another%20critical%20fertiliser%20used%20in%20industrial%20agriculture.%20NU%20and%20nano-DAP%20are%20presented%20as%20saviours%20against%20the%20rising%20fertilisers%20import%20bill.%20The%20Union%20government%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Findia-aims-to-replace-25-of-urea-imports-with-locally-produced-nano-urea-by-2025-saving-up-to-20-000-crore-annually-says-union-fertilizer-secretary-11680716628426.html%23%3A~%3Atext%3DIndia%2C%2520the%2520top%2520importer%2520of%2Cat%2520%246.5%2520billion%2520in%2520FY22.%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eclaimed%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20NU%20will%20save%20%E2%80%9CRs%2015%2C000-20%2C000%20crore%20annually%E2%80%9D%20and%20perhaps%20that%E2%80%99s%20why%20it%20is%20forcing%20farmers%20in%20Gujarat%20and%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20country%20to%20forcefully%20adopt%20IFFCO%E2%80%99s%20NU%20and%20curtailing%20the%20urea%20bags%20allotment.%20Farmers%20in%20Kutch%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fahmedabad%2Fkutch-farmers-not-in-favour-of-nano-urea-oppose-mandatory-sale-8892791%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eprotested%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3Eagainst%20this%20move%20and%20didn%E2%80%99t%20like%20the%20mandatory%20imposition%2C%20especially%20on%20Independence%20Day.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F05%2F26171336%2Fdap.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F05%2F26171336%2Fdap.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F05%2F26171336%2Fdap-300x150.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F05%2F26171336%2Fdap-1024x513.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F05%2F26171336%2Fdap-800x400.jpg%20800w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-530667%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22601%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERepresentative%20image%20of%20a%20farmer%20spraying%20fertiliser.%20Photo%3A%20IFPRI%2FFlickr%20CC%20BY%20NC%20ND%202.0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EScience%20against%20nano%20urea%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20get%20a%20deeper%20insight%20into%20the%20problem%2C%20I%20spoke%20with%20the%20authors%20of%20the%20recent%20paper%2C%20Frank%20and%20Husted.%20They%20explained%20what%20will%20happen%20after%20NU%20is%20realised%20on%20a%20mass%20scale%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20next%20one%20or%20two%20years%2C%20we%E2%80%99d%20expect%20the%20nitrogen%20stocks%20present%20in%20soils%20from%20previous%20fertilisation%20to%20decline%2C%20while%20the%20yields%20remain%20more%20or%20less%20stable%20%E2%80%93%20whether%20you%20add%20NU%20or%20not.%20After%20the%20second%20or%20third%20year%2C%20the%20nitrogen%20from%20previous%20years%20is%20used%20up%20more%20and%20more%20and%20the%20stock%20would%20become%20so%20low%20that%20we%20would%20start%20to%20expect%20a%20massive%20decline%20in%20crop%20productivity.%20The%20nitrogen%20deficit%20cannot%20be%20filled%20up%20by%20NU.%20That%20is%20a%20simple%20mass%20balance%20%E2%80%93%2021kg%20nitrogen%20from%20urea%20versus%2020%20g%20from%20NU%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20explained.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CA%20mass-scale%20adoption%20of%20NU%20would%20result%20in%20large-scale%20yield%20losses%20if%20it%20replaces%20conventional%20urea%20(45kg%20bag%20to%20500%20ml%20NU).%20Ultimately%2C%20loss%20of%20food%20security%20and%20the%20livelihood%20of%20farmers%20is%20to%20be%20expected.%20This%20will%20also%20erode%20the%20trust%20in%20agricultural%20science%20and%20plant%20mistrust%20in%20novel%20sustainable%20technologies%20that%20we%20need%20so%20urgently%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20scientists%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscience.thewire.in%2Fthe-sciences%2Fnano-urea-crop-yield-doubts%2F%5C%22%3ENano%20Urea%3A%20Scientists%20Doubt%20Purported%20Benefits%20of%20Fertiliser%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20also%20important%20to%20understand%20the%20technical%20gaps%20in%20IFFCO%E2%80%99s%20claims.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20most%20common%20error%20is%20the%20choice%20of%20the%20adequate%20control%20treatment.%20On%20their%20website%2C%20IFFCO%20recommends%20farmers%20replace%20top-dressed%2Ffoliar%20urea%20with%20two%20sprays%20of%20top-dressed%2Ffoliar%20NU%20(45kg%20vs%20500%20ml).%20However%2C%20this%20has%20never%20been%20investigated%20in%20any%20field%20trial.%20IFFCO%20has%20investigated%20a%20replacement%20of%20soil-applied%20urea%20by%202x%20top-dressed%20NU%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20duo%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CMedia%20and%20public%20outreach%20of%20IFFCO%20report%20that%20farmers%20can%20generally%20replace%20a%20bag%20of%20urea%20with%20a%20bottle%20of%20NU.%20However%2C%20it%20is%20highly%20probable%20that%20farmers%20could%20replace%20a%20bag%20of%20urea%20with%20nothing%2C%20or%20with%20a%20spray%20of%20conventional%20urea%2C%20and%20they%20would%20still%20have%20the%20same%20yields.%20This%20has%20never%20been%20investigated%20properly%2C%20either%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20conclusion%2C%20they%20emphasised%20that%20the%20conclusions%20of%20the%20papers%20do%20not%20fit%20the%20treatments%20applied%20in%20the%20field%20studies%2C%20and%20IFFCO%E2%80%99s%20claims%20do%20not%20fit%20the%20conclusions%20and%20treatments%20in%20the%20papers%2C%20either.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20also%20point%20out%20how%20%E2%80%9Cmost%20field%20trials%20have%20been%20conducted%20for%20only%20one%20season%20%E2%80%93%20this%20does%20not%20account%20for%20soil%2C%20weather%2C%20and%20climate%20variability.%E2%80%9D%20Field%20trials%20typically%20need%20to%20be%20undertaken%20for%20different%20cultivars%20in%20many%20regions%2C%20in%20different%20soils%20and%20over%20several%20years.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20few%C2%A0field%20trials%C2%A0conducted%20for%20two%20seasons%C2%A0weren%E2%80%99t%C2%A0undertaken%20in%20the%20same%20place.%20That%20is%20why%20%E2%80%9Cmost%20results%20do%20not%20seem%20statistically%20significant%2C%20and%20often%2C%20no%20statistics%20were%20applied%20at%20all%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20them%2C%20increased%20yields%20because%20of%20NU%20remained%20unproven.%20Plus%20the%20development%20of%20the%20soil%E2%80%99s%20nitrogen%20pool%20and%20its%20uptake%20from%20the%20crops%20through%20NU%20was%20not%20investigated%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20such%20a%20trial%20to%20have%20a%20value%2C%20the%20soil%20needs%20to%20be%20nitrogen-responsive.%20That%20means%2C%20that%20the%20addition%20of%20nitrogen%20with%20a%20fertiliser%20will%20indeed%20result%20in%20an%20increased%20yield.%20Many%20field%20trials%20fail%20to%20show%20that%20soils%20were%20indeed%20nitrogen-responsive.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOverall%2C%20they%20concluded%20that%20it%20is%20%E2%80%9Cvery%20poorly%20described%20in%20which%20way%20the%20crops%20were%20treated.%E2%80%9D%20Statements%20remain%20very%20general%20and%20unscientific%2C%20such%20as%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20treatment%20was%20undertaken%20as%20per%20crop%20yields%E2%80%9D.%20This%20does%20not%20contain%20any%20valuable%20information.%20And%20went%20on%20to%20say%20claims%20are%20%E2%80%9Coften%20based%20on%20older%20claims%20in%20other%20papers%20that%20do%20not%20even%20deal%20with%20the%20topic%20%E2%80%93%20so%20scientific%20referencing%20is%20wrong%20and%20misleading%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20India%20connection%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThrough%20the%20paper%20and%20my%20conversation%20with%20its%20author%2C%20it%20became%20clear%20that%20there%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.researchgate.net%2Fpublication%2F372217319_Productivity_of_Wheat_as_influenced_by_foliar_spray_of_IFFCO_nano_urea%5C%22%3Emounting%20evidence%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20NU%20or%20its%20claimed%20benefit%20for%20farmers%20or%20food%20production%2C%20and%20much%20of%20this%20comes%20from%20India.%20The%20name%20of%20former%20soil%20scientist%20N.K.%20Tomar%20from%20Chaudhary%20Charan%20Singh%20Haryana%20State%20Agricultural%20University%20came%20up%20repeatedly%20in%20this%20context.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CNano%20urea%20is%20a%20complete%20fraud.%20I%20have%20tested%20the%20product%20in%20my%20own%20fields%20and%20seen%20the%20results.%20I%20had%20even%20offered%20my%20own%20fields%20to%20government-run%20research%20institutes%20for%20doing%20field%20trials%20of%20NU%2C%20but%20received%20no%20reply.%20It%20is%20because%20the%20government%20knows%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20fraud%20product%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Tomar%2C%20who%20now%20lives%20on%20his%20farm%20in%20Meerut.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CDevelopment%20of%20NU%2C%20nano%20DAP%20and%20nano%20zinc%20sulfate%2C%20etc.%20and%20IIFCO%E2%80%99s%20baseless%20claims%20about%20their%20efficiency%20is%20the%20biggest%20fraud%20in%20the%20history%20of%20science.%20All%20the%20relevant%20universal%2C%20fundamental%20principles%20of%20chemistry%2C%20plant%20nutrition%20and%20plant%20physiology%20were%20ignored%20and%20overlooked%20in%20this%20activity%2C%20including%20permission%20for%20their%20sale%20(marketing)%20and%20recommendation%20for%20use%20by%20the%20farmers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETomar%20explained%20the%20problem%20with%20a%20simple%20formula.%20%E2%80%9CIFFCO%20recommends%20using%2020g%20NU%20in%20half%20a%20litre%20solution%20for%20foliar%20spray%20on%20a%201-acre%20field.%20This%20area%20usually%20requires%20about%20150%20litres%20of%20water.%20This%20is%20equal%20to%200.0133%25%20NU%20solution%20as%20opposed%20to%202%25%20normal%20urea%20solution%20that%20has%20been%20sprayed%20on%20crops%20for%20more%20than%2060%20years.%20Thus%2C%20the%20NU%20solution%20is%20150%20times%20more%20dilute%20than%20the%20normal%20urea%20solution.%20Even%20if%20the%20plant%20absorbs%20all%20of%20the%20urea%20(which%20is%20quite%20impossible)%20the%20urea%20to%20wheat%20protein%20ratio%20cannot%20be%20maintained%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EErratic%20weather%2C%20expensive%20fertilisers%2C%20hyper-food%20inflation%20and%20the%20Ukraine-Russia%20conflict%20coupled%20with%20Indian%20farmers%20being%20pushed%20to%20adopt%20a%20fake%20solution%20can%20only%20spell%20out%20disaster%20for%20food%20security%20in%20the%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Findra-shekhar-singh%5C%22%3EIndra%20Shekhar%20Singh%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20former%20director%2C%20policy%20and%20outreach%2C%20the%20National%20Seed%20Association%20of%20India.%20He%20tweets%20at%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Findrassingh%5C%22%3E%40Indrassingh%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693310444000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F02%2F08200430%2Fimage1-2.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Fnano-urea-project-efficiency-questions%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22There%20is%20mounting%20evidence%20against%20the%20efficacy%20of%20nano%20urea%20or%20its%20claimed%20benefits%20for%20farmers%20or%20food%20production%2C%20and%20much%20of%20this%20comes%20from%20India.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Fnano-urea-project-efficiency-questions%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rajesh%20Pilot%20Did%20Not%20Fly%20the%20IAF%20Plane%20That%20Bombed%20Mizoram%20in%201966%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F29154546%2FIndian_Air_Force_flag_at_India_Gate.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20reply%20to%20the%20no-confidence%20motion%20brought%20by%20the%20opposition%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20recently%20