resh%20Kalmadi.%E2%80%9D.%20The%20same%20article%20was%20also%20published%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20221202192246%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Fsg-national-interest%2Fthe-buck-starts-here%2F544156%2F%5C%22%3Ewebsite%20of%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Print%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20of%20which%20Gupta%20is%20the%20founding%20editor.%20A%20number%20of%20other%20websites%20have%20also%20made%20the%20same%20claim%20citing%20this%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20article%20as%20their%20source.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F29152521%2FUntitled-design-3-3.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F29152521%2FUntitled-design-3-3.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F29152521%2FUntitled-design-3-3-300x232.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F29152521%2FUntitled-design-3-3-1024x792.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-670446%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22928%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShekhar%20Gupta%20repeated%20the%20same%20claim%20in%20a%20tweet%20dated%20July%2015%2C%202020%20and%20stated%20that%20in%20early%201966%20when%20the%20Mizo%20insurgency%20started%20and%20it%20looked%20like%20Aizawl%20would%20fall%2C%20Mrs%20Gandhi%2C%20who%20had%20been%20prime%20minister%20for%20a%20few%20weeks%2C%20sent%20the%20IAF%20to%20stop%20the%20rebels.%20He%20added%20that%20transport%20aircraft%20like%20Caribus%20were%20also%20used%20in%20this%20attack%2C%20and%20were%20being%20flown%20by%20Rajesh%20Pilot%20with%20Suresh%20Kalmadi%20as%20the%20navigator.%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20220721092028%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FShekharGupta%2Fstatus%2F1283404097899524096%5C%22%3EArchived%20link%3C%2Fa%3E)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F29152614%2FScreenshot-2023-08-23-160050.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22952%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F29152614%2FScreenshot-2023-08-23-160050.png%20952w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F29152614%2FScreenshot-2023-08-23-160050-300x217.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-670447%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22688%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EShekhar%20Gupta%E2%80%99s%20columns%20updated%20with%20correct%20information%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20August%2017%2C%202023%2C%20%3Cem%3EAlt%20News%3C%2Fem%3E%20reached%20out%20to%20Shekhar%20Gupta%20and%20asked%20him%20about%20the%20source%20of%20information%20for%20the%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20column%20and%20his%20tweet%20where%20he%20had%20made%20the%20claim%20about%20Rajesh%20Pilot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20August%2021%2C%202023%2C%20the%202010%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20article%20was%20updated%20to%20remove%20the%20claim%20that%20Rajesh%20Pilot%20was%20involved%20in%20the%20March%201966%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20bombings%20of%20Aizawl.%20Along%20with%20this%2C%20Shekhar%20Gupta%20wrote%20in%20the%20Indian%20Express%20column%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20got%20mixed%20up%20with%20my%20dates%20and%20periods%20and%20erred%20in%20including%20his%20(Rajesh%20Pilot%E2%80%99s)%20name.%20Accordingly%2C%20corrections%20are%20made%20in%20my%20archived%20article%20published%20above.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGupta%20also%20updated%20his%20column%20on%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Print%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99s%20website%20and%20removed%20the%20line%20that%20claimed%20that%20Rajesh%20Pilot%20was%20involved%20in%20the%20bombing%20of%20Aizawl%20by%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force.%20Along%20with%20this%2C%20he%20gave%20a%20clarification%20regarding%20this.%20What%20he%20mentioned%20in%20his%20column%20was%20based%20on%20several%20conversations%20he%20had%20from%20time%20to%20time%20with%20pilots%20of%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20of%20that%20time%2C%20including%20Rajesh%20Pilot.%20He%20got%20confused%20over%20the%20dates%20and%20periods%20of%20many%20talks%20which%20he%20regrets%20and%20admits%20he%20made%20a%20mistake.%20He%20further%20added%20that%20corrections%20had%20been%20made%20in%20his%20article%20originally%20published%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20August%2023%2C%202023%20he%20replied%20to%20%3Cem%3EAlt%20News%3C%2Fem%3E%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20look%20at%20the%20relevant%20column%20on%20the%20Indian%20Express%20website%2C%20you%20will%20find%20the%20answers%20you%20are%20looking%20for.%20You%20can%20also%20find%20them%20in%20some%20degree%20of%20detail%20on%20The%20Print.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20updated%20part%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20article%20can%20be%20seen%20here%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F29152907%2FScreenshot-2023-08-23-162643.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221188%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F29152907%2FScreenshot-2023-08-23-162643.jpg%201188w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F29152907%2FScreenshot-2023-08-23-162643-300x293.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F29152907%2FScreenshot-2023-08-23-162643-1024x1000.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-670450%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%2211