ps%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Fcentre-announces-up-to-rs-50-lakh-grant-for-technical-textiles-startups-123082900683_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Fcentre-announces-up-to-rs-50-lakh-grant-for-technical-textiles-startups-123082900683_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kathua%20Teacher%20Arrested%20For%20Beating%20up%20Class%2010%20Student%20Over%20'Jai%20Shri%20Ram'%20on%20Blackboard%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F29161240%2FScreenshot-2023-08-29-at-4.09.27.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESrinagar%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Authorities%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20have%20arrested%20a%20teacher%20of%20a%20government%20higher%20secondary%20school%20in%20Bani%20of%20Kathua%20district%20for%20allegedly%20severely%20beating%20up%20a%20Class%2010%20student%20because%20he%20wrote%20%E2%80%98Jai%20Shri%20Ram%E2%80%99%20on%20the%20class%20blackboard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20teacher%20and%20the%20principal%20of%20the%20school%20were%20both%20also%20suspended.%20The%20government%20has%20ordered%C2%A0two%20separate%20enquiries%20into%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20first%20information%20report%20(FIR)%20registered%20by%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20police%20in%20the%20case%2C%20the%20father%20of%20the%20juvenile%20has%20claimed%20that%20his%20son%2C%20a%20student%20of%20Class%2010%2C%20was%20beaten%20severely%20by%20the%20teacher%20and%20principal%20of%20the%20Government%20Higher%20Secondary%20School%20at%20Bani%20for%20writing%20%E2%80%98Jai%20Shri%20Ram%E2%80%99%20slogan%20on%20blackboard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20father%20said%20in%20the%20complaint%20that%20at%20around%20noon%20on%20August%2025%20(Friday)%20when%20teacher%20Farooq%20Ahmad%20entered%20the%20classroom%2C%20he%20found%20that%20%E2%80%98Jai%20Shri%20Ram%E2%80%99%20was%20written%20on%20the%20blackboard.%20He%20then%2C%20allegedly%2C%20beat%20the%20boy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20father%20claimed%20that%20Ahmad%20then%20then%20took%20the%20minor%20to%20the%20office%20of%20the%20principal%20and%20that%20he%20was%20beaten%20up%20there%20by%20Ahmad%20and%20principal%20Muhammad%20Hafeez.%20The%20room%20was%20locked%20during%20the%20beating%2C%20the%20complaint%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20juvenile%20was%20admitted%20to%20the%20hospital%20for%20treatment%2C%20it%20further%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSomeone%20called%20me%20over%20the%20phone%20on%20August%2025%20and%20told%20me%20that%20my%20son%20has%20been%20thrashed%20in%20the%20school.%20I%20immediately%20left%20home%20and%20trekked%20on%20foot%20to%20reach%20his%20rented%20accommodation.%20I%20was%20shocked%20to%20find%20him%20writhing%20in%20pain%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20boy%E2%80%99s%20father%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20triggered%20protests%20by%20students%20on%20August%2026.%20Several%20local%20leaders%20also%20visited%20the%20institution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20have%20registered%20an%20FIR%20under%20sections%20323%20(voluntarily%20causing%20hurt)%2C%20342%20(wrongful%20confinement)%2C%20504%20(intentional%20insult%20to%20provoke%20breach%20of%20peace)%20and%20506%20(criminal%20intimidation)%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20against%20the%20duo%20at%20the%20Bani%20police%20station.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20these%2C%20section%2075%20of%20Juvenile%20Justice%20(Care%20and%20Protection%20of%20Children)%20Act%2C%202015%2C%20have%20also%20been%20added%20to%20the%20FIR.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStation%20House%20Officer%20of%20the%20Bani%20Police%20Station%2C%20Arjun%20Magotra%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20police%20have%20registered%20an%20FIR%20in%20the%20incident%20and%20arrested%20the%20teacher.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20authorities%20of%20school%20education%20department%20have%20placed%20Farooq%20Ahmad%20and%20Muhammad%20Hafeez%20under%20suspension%20and%20ordered%20an%20enquiry%20by%20Director%20of%20School%20Education%20at%20Jammu%20into%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20order%20for%20suspension%20by%20the%20department%20was%20issued%20on%20August%2026%2C%20the%20day%20when%20the%20family%20of%20the%20boy%20registered%20a%20complaint%20in%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20district%20administration%20of%20Kathua%20has%20also%20ordered%20a%20separate%20enquiry%20in%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20order%2C%20the%20Deputy%20Commissioner%20of%20Kathua%20has%20constituted%20a%20three-member%20committee%20comprising%20sub-divisional%20magistrate%2C%20deputy%20chief%20education%20officer%20Kathua%20(Billawar)%20and%20Principal%20Government%20Higher%20Secondary%20School%2C%20Kharote%2C%20to%20enquire%20into%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20committee%20has%20been%20directed%20to%20submit%20a%20fact-finding%20report%20along%20with%20specific%20comments%20and%20recommendations%20for%20proceeding%20in%20the%20matter%2C%20apart%20from%20fixing%20the%20responsibility%20against%20the%20culprit(s)%20in%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20the%20incident%2C%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20former%20CM%20Mehbooba%20Mufti%20said%20that%20hate-mongers%20won%E2%80%99t%20even%20spare%20kids%20and%20appreciated%20police%20for%20prompt%20action%20in%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHate%20mongers%20won%E2%80%99t%20even%20spare%20kids%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20their%20venomous%20mindset.%20Appreciate%20the%20prompt%20action%20taken%20by%20Kathua%20police%20in%20filing%20an%20FIR.%20Odd%20that%20in%20the%20UP%20case%2C%20police%20is%20pressurising%20the%20child%E2%80%99s%20father%20to%20drop%20charges%20against%20the%20teacher%20who%20encouraged%20students%20to%20thrash%20him%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20tweeted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%E2%80%9CUP%20case%E2%80%9D%20that%20Mufti%20is%20referring%20to%20came%20to%20light%20when%20a%20video%20showing%20the%20principal%20of%20a%20school%20forcing%20students%20to%20hit%20their%20Muslim%20classmate%20for%20not%20having%20learnt%20maths%20tables%20went%20viral.%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reported%20on%20how%20this%20student%E2%80%99s%20family%20is%20being%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fup-pressure-on-boys-family-to-compromise-in-slapping-incident-as-politicians-swarm-the-village%5C%22%3Epushed%20to%20strike%20a%20compromise.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693305952000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F29161240%2FScreenshot-2023-08-29-at-4.09.27.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fjammu-kashmir-teacher-arrested-beating-student%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20teacher%20and%20the%20principal%20of%20the%20school%20have%20both%20been%20suspended.%20The%20government%20has%20ordered%C2%A0two%20separate%20enquiries%20into%20the%20matter.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fjammu-kashmir-teacher-arrested-beating-student%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Centre%20cuts%20LPG%20cylinders%20price%20by%20Rs%20200%20for%20PMUY%20beneficiaries%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693305409000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2022-03%2F17%2Ffull%2F1647523615-4048.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-to-cut-lpg-cylinders-price-by-rs-200-for-pmuy-beneficiaries-report-123082900620_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20July%2C%20oil%20companies%20increased%20the%20price%20of%20domestic%20LPG%20cylinders%20by%20Rs%2050.%20Earlier%2C%20the%20prices%20were%20increased%20twice%20in%20the%20month%20of%20May%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-to-cut-lpg-cylinders-price-by-rs-200-for-pmuy-beneficiaries-report-123082900620_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-to-cut-lpg-cylinders-price-by-rs-200-for-pmuy-beneficiaries-report-123082900620_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-to-cut-lpg-cylinders-price-by-rs-200-for-pmuy-beneficiaries-report-123082900620_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Nepal%20Continues%20to%20Spend%20Big%20on%20Buying%20Electricity%20From%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F04%2F29175353%2FPOWER-L-PTI.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3ENepal%20continues%20to%20spend%20more%20in%20buying%20electricity%20from%20India%20than%20earning%20through%20its%20export%2C%20even%20as%20the%20country%20aims%20to%20become%20a%20net%20exporter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20domestic%20production%20declines%20sharply%20in%20the%20dry%20season%20requiring%20power%20supply%20from%20the%20southern%20neighbour%2C%20the%20Nepal%20Electricity%20Authority%20(NEA)%20has%20been%20forced%20to%20spend%20big%20on%20buying%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20NEA%2C%20it%20spent%20as%20much%20Rs%201%2C944%20crore%20to%20buy%20power%20from%20India%20while%20its%20export%20to%20the%20southern%20neighbour%20stood%20at%20Rs%201%2C010%20crore%20in%20the%20last%20fiscal%20year%202022-23%2C%20suggesting%20the%20country%20still%20has%20a%20long%20way%20to%20go%20to%20be%20self-reliant%20in%20clean%20energy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENepal%20exported%20power%20equivalent%20to%201%2C333%20gigawatt%20hours%20in%20the%20last%20fiscal%20while%20it%20imported%201%2C833%20gigawatt%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProlonged%20drought%20in%20the%20last%20fiscal%20year%20badly%20affected%20domestic%20power%20generation%20and%20the%20country%20had%20to%20import%20more%2C%20said%20Kul%20Man%20Ghising%2C%20managing%20director%20of%20the%20NEA.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20result%2C%20Nepal%20continues%20to%20become%20a%20net%20importer.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStating%20that%20the%20country%20faced%20an%20unprecedented%20fall%20in%20power%20generation%2C%20the%20NEA%20decided%20to%20procure%20power%20through%20bids%20from%20Indian%20generators%20and%20traders%20with%20the%20hope%20that%20competition%20would%20significantly%20lower%20the%20purchase%20price%20of%20electricity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20since%20the%20lowest%20bid%20prices%20exceeded%20the%20average%20price%20trends%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20day-ahead%20power%20exchange%20market%2C%20the%20NEA%20was%20bound%20to%20annul%20the%20bidding%20process%20and%20cling%20to%20a%20bilateral%20agreement%20with%20the%20Indian%20power%20traders%20for%20the%20months%20of%20March%2C%20April%20and%20May%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20power%20utility%20said%20in%20its%20Annual%20Report%202022-23.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20fiscal%20year%202019-20%2C%20Nepal%E2%80%99s%20power%20import%20has%20been%20on%20a%20downward%20trend%20amid%20increasing%20domestic%20power%20generation%20in%20the%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGhising%20said%20that%20he%20believes%20power%20imports%20will%20continue%20to%20decline%20even%20though%20the%20country%20had%20to%20import%20more%20due%20to%20prolonged%20drought.%20%E2%80%9CStill%2C%20net%20import%20decreased%20even%20in%20the%20last%20fiscal%20year%2C%20even%20though%20total%20imports%20increased%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NEA%20aims%20to%20be%20self-reliant%20on%20electricity%20by%202026.%20Ghising%20said%20it%20was%20possible%20to%20meet%20this%20target%20considering%20the%20planned%20generation%20of%20the%20electricity%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20end%20of%20the%20current%20fiscal%20year%202022-23%2C%20Nepal%E2%80%99s%20power%20generation%20capacity%20is%20expected%20to%20reach%202%2C853%20MW%2C%204%2C507%20MW%20by%20mid-July%202024%20and%205%2C251%20MW%20in%20mid-July%202025%2C%20according%20to%20the%20power%20utility.%20But%20domestic%20consumption%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20half%20the%20potential%20generation%20by%202025%2C%20forcing%20Nepal%20to%20sell%20electricity%20abroad%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20all%20the%20planned%20projects%20are%20completed%20by%202026%2C%20Nepal%20has%20every%20chance%20of%20becoming%20self-reliant%20on%20electricity%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Sher%20Singh%20Bhat%2C%20former%20deputy%20managing%20director%20of%20the%20NEA.%20%E2%80%9CProvided%20Nepal%20achieves%20generation%20capacity%20of%20around%205%2C500%20MW%2C%20there%20can%20be%20base%20load%20demand%20for%20around%202%2C000%20MW%20in%20the%20dry%20season%20which%20Nepal%20can%20meet%20with%20its%20own%20generation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20him%2C%20the%20country%20can%20also%20fulfil%20the%20peak%20power%20demands%2C%20of%20around%203%2C000%20MW%2C%20through%20peaking%20power%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20bigger%20worry%20is%20whether%20the%20country%20can%20increase%20its%20power%20export%20given%20the%20transmission%20constraints%20and%20uncertainty%20about%20India%20consistently%20buying%20Nepal%E2%80%99s%20electricity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Prime%20Minister%20Pushpa%20Kamal%20Dahal%20visited%20India%20in%20May%20and%20June%2C%20New%20Delhi%20had%20announced%20that%20it%20would%20buy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fkathmandupost.com%2Fmoney%2F2023%2F06%2F11%2Fhow-nepal-can-sell-10-000mw-power%5C%22%3E10%2C000%20MW%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20next%20ten%20years.%20But%20the%20southern%20neighbour%20is%20yet%20to%20grant%20Nepal%20additional%20export%20permission%20after%20earlier%20approving%20452.6%20MW.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20a%20question%20of%20whether%20India%20will%20be%20a%20reliable%20trading%20partner%20of%20electricity%20as%20it%20has%20come%20to%20treat%20power%20as%20a%20strategic%20product%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bhat%20said.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20thus%20important%20to%20sustainably%20increase%20domestic%20demands%20as%20we%20will%20continue%20to%20rely%20on%20ourselves%20for%20the%20consumption%20of%20electricity%20we%20produce.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EPrithvi%20Man%20Shrestha%20is%20a%20political%20reporter%20for%3C%2Fem%3E%20The%20Kathmandu%20Post%3Cem%3E%2C%20covering%20the%20governance-related%20issues%20including%20corruption%20and%20irregularities%20in%20the%20government%20machinery.%20Before%20joining%20%3C%2Fem%3EThe%20Kathmandu%20Post%20%3Cem%3Ein%202009%2C%20he%20worked%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3Enepalnews.com%3Cem%3E%20and%20%3C%2Fem%3ERising%20Nepal%3Cem%3E%2C%20primarily%20covering%20the%20issues%20of%20political%20and%20economic%20affairs%20for%20three%20years.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20originally%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fkathmandupost.com%2Fnational%2F2023%2F08%2F29%2Fnepal-continues-to-be-net-importer-of-electricity%5C%22%3Epublished%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%3C%2Fem%3E%20The%20Kathmandu%20Post.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693304473000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F04%2F29175353%2FPOWER-L-PTI.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenergy%2Fnepal-continues-to-spend-big-on-buying-electricity-from-india%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nepal%20spent%20around%20Rs%201%2C944%20crore%20on%20buying%20electricity%20from%20India%20while%20its%20exports%20stood%20at%20Rs%201%2C010%20crore%20in%202022-23.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenergy%2Fnepal-continues-to-spend-big-on-buying-electricity-from-india%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22NSD%20Postpones%20'Tamas'%20Performance%20After%20Social%20Media%20Campaign%20Spurred%20by%20BJP%20Ex-MP%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F11%2F23121335%2F29261176_1885312504844120_2521931292140896256_n.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0The%20National%20School%20of%20Drama%20has%20indefinitely%20postponed%20the%20performance%20of%20Bhisham%20Sahni%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3ETamas%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20days%20after%20a%20social%20media%20campaign%20was%20led%20by%20accounts%20linked%20to%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20against%20the%20choice%20of%20the%20play%2C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fcities%2FDelhi%2Fnsd-postpones-shows-of-play-based-on-bhisham-sahnis-tamas%2Farticle67245129.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%20The%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20says%20that%20the%20NSD%20Repertory%20was%20supposed%20to%20stage%20the%20play%20at%20the%20Abhimanch%20Auditorium%20from%20August%2014%20to%2020.%20It%20was%20to%20be%20part%20of%20its%20end-of-the-session%20show%2C%20for%20which%20close%20to%20two%20months%20of%20rehearsals%20had%20already%20taken%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20days%20before%20the%20show%20opened%2C%20the%20institution%20put%20up%20a%20statement%20on%20social%20media%20announcing%20the%20postponement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETamas%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Ewritten%20in%20Hindi%2C%20is%20a%20hard-hitting%20and%20famous%20novel%20on%20the%20Partition%20of%20India%20and%20the%20communal%20politics%20at%20play%20at%20the%20time.%20It%20focuses%20on%20the%20effect%20of%20such%20politics%20on%20ordinary%20people.%20It%20has%20earlier%20been%20produced%20on%20television.%20Sahni%20is%20a%20Padma%20Bhushan%20recipient.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Cem%3EHindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%20notes%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20social%20media%20campaign%20was%20kick-started%20by%20a%20message%20on%20a%20chat%20group%20by%20former%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20Balbir%20Punj.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPunj%20called%20Sahni%20a%20leftist%20in%20his%20message%20and%20claimed%20that%20Tamas%20had%20%E2%80%9Cdirectly%20or%20indirectly%E2%80%9D%20held%20the%20RSS%20responsible%20for%20communal%20violence%20during%20that%20time.%20This%2C%20Punj%20claimed%20in%20the%20message%2C%20was%20%E2%80%9Cfactually%20wrong%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%20to%20%3Cem%3EHindu%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Punj%20said%20he%20said%20%E2%80%9Cwhat%20%5Bhe%5D%20wanted%20to%20say%20in%20the%20message%20posted%20on%20the%20chat%20group%E2%80%9D%20and%20didn%E2%80%99t%20wish%20to%20comment%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20message%2C%20the%20report%20says%2C%20made%20its%20way%20around%20several%20chat%20groups%2C%20and%20then%20on%20to%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20and%20other%20public%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParticipants%20in%20this%20campaign%20often%20tagged%20Union%20ministers%20Arjun%20Ram%20Meghwal%20and%20Meenakshi%20Lekhi%2C%20who%20were%20slated%20to%20appear%20as%20special%20guests%20for%20the%20opening%20show%20on%20August%2014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENSD%20Repertory%E2%80%99s%20chief%20Rajesh%20Singh%20told%20the%20paper%20that%20the%20show%20has%20not%20been%20cancelled%20but%20postponed%20due%20to%20%E2%80%9Csome%20internal%20reason%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESingh%20said%20he%20did%20not%20know%20if%20the%20social%20media%20buzz%20contributed%20to%20the%20postponement.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693302941000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F11%2F23121335%2F29261176_1885312504844120_2521931292140896256_n.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fthe-arts%2Fnational-school-of-drama-bhisham-sahni-tamas-bjp%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20his%20message%20on%20a%20group%2C%20Balbir%20Punj%20had%20called%20writer%20Bhisham%20Sahni%20a%20leftist%20and%20claimed%20that%20'Tamas'%20had%20%E2%80%9Cdirectly%20or%20indirectly%E2%80%9D%20held%20the%20RSS%20responsible%20for%20communal%20violence%20during%20Parition.%22%2C%22author