d%20across%20countries%20like%20the%20US%2C%20Canada%2C%20Japan%20and%20seen%20scientists%20working%20hard%20to%20develop%20technologies%20for%20agricultural%20advancements%20at%20home.%20However%2C%20India%20did%20not%20have%20%5Ban%20indigenous%5D%20hydroponics%20technology.%20While%20there%20are%20startups%20that%20are%20using%20hydroponics%2C%20they%20are%20mostly%20exported%20by%20Israel%20or%20Japan%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20notes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EIncreasing%20the%20food%20productivity%20of%20India%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20former%20student%20and%20a%20university%20faculty%20member%2C%20Dr%20Sethi%20has%20dedicated%20nearly%20three%20decades%20of%20his%20life%20to%20researching%20and%20developing%20sustainable%20technologies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FPAU-1-1692278262.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20technology%20claims%20to%20save%2090%20percent%20of%20water%20through%20recirculation%20mode.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FPAU-1-1692278262.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FPAU-1-1692278262-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FPAU-1-1692278262-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FPAU-1-1692278262-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FPAU-1-1692278262-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-327481%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20technology%20claims%20to%20save%2090%20percent%20of%20water%20through%20recirculation%20mode.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20V%20P%20Sethi%20%3C%2Ffigcap